Trendy footwear brand Footwork has collaborated with K Naomi for its Spring Summer 18 collection This pairing comes as no surprise, as Footwork has been observing K Naomi’s distinct aesthetic and evolution for some time. It has now teamed up with the presenter, fashionista and budding influencer as the representative for the brand’s bold, instinctual and fashionable customer.   READ MORE: Five types of shoes every woman should own   READ MORE: Before you buy shoes  Watch as K Naomi talks about her partnership with Footwork, building her own brand and choosing to work with brands that share her values. 